        # Jaisa example 3 mein "b" two index mein hai, 1 aur 5 aur "B" ekh index mein, 2. agar ham sirf index() use karta hai toh 1<2 check hoga and agar ham rindex() use karta hai toh 5<2, joki correct hai 

